import Mathlib.Tactic
import Mathlib.Data.Nat.Factorial.DoubleFactorial

/-!
# The char-0 additive energy `E_28(μ_n)`: exact closed form (#444, avenue L2)

This extends the verified char-0 closed-form ladder one rung beyond `E_26` and the concurrent
`E_27` lane. It records the exact cross-polytope / Lam--Leung polynomial at depth `r = 28`,
plus the Wick bound and a strict positive cushion. The positivity certificate starts at
`n = 9`, covering the dyadic support range `n = 2`, `n = 4`, `n = 8`, or `n ≥ 9`. This is deliberately
only a char-0 rung; it does not assert the char-p transfer that forms the #444 BGK/Paley wall.
-/

namespace ProximityGap.Frontier.E28ClosedForm

/-- `E_28(ℂ)(n)`: the char-0 additive energy of `μ_n` at depth `r = 28`, in closed form. -/
